  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/036e7f0d465368e2eae30dd20f6f26f9.poster.avif?t=1745903625\" width=594 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/036e7f0d465368e2eae30dd20f6f26f9.webm?t=1745903625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/036e7f0d465368e2eae30dd20f6f26f9.mp4?t=1745903625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i> </i><br>A throwback to the quarter-munching arcade hits of the '80s, <strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong> is a fast-paced, addictive shoot 'em up with a modern twist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/8c1acbfa8e0b7550c37dbeb9454ce2e0.apng?t=1745903625\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/8c1acbfa8e0b7550c37dbeb9454ce2e0.poster.avif?t=1745903625\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=41 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ship <strong>never stops moving</strong>, turn, boost, and brake to dodge enemies and stay alive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fire automatically</strong> - focus on dodging and collecting power-ups.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gather ammo and power-ups</strong> to unleash devastating attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn coins</strong> to unlock new ships, each with unique speed, fire rate, and shields.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chase high scores</strong> in endless survival mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/43822ef3d3ca31baffe2ef48e0d82bd8.apng?t=1745903625\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/43822ef3d3ca31baffe2ef48e0d82bd8.poster.avif?t=1745903625\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=41 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to Learn, Hard to Master</strong> – Simple controls, deep gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Twin-Stick Needed</strong> – Classic arcade-style movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Massive Power-Ups</strong> – Heat-seekers, lasers, spread shots, bombs, shields, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Ships</strong> – Each with distinct playstyles and advantages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bullet Hell Intensity</strong> – Dodge waves of enemies and projectiles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards & Achievements</strong> – Compete for the top spot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong> – Earn emoticons & profile wallpapers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Cloud Support</strong> – Pick up where you left off.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Languages</strong> – Available in English, Russian, German, Italian, Portuguese, French, Simplified Chinese, and Spanish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Soundtrack by Spiff Tune</strong> – Unique chiptunes for each ship (free DLC).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired by the Best: </strong>Classic hits like <strong>Luftrausers, Asteroids, Space Invaders, Galaxian,</strong> and <strong>Geometry Wars</strong> influence <strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong>’s addictive gameplay and retro charm.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/af15f1c837a8edc3e7adb90689e8980d.apng?t=1745903625\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/af15f1c837a8edc3e7adb90689e8980d.poster.avif?t=1745903625\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=41 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong> is a simple, replayable score-chaser designed for arcade fun. If you find an issue or just want to say hi, reach out via Discord or my website, I appreciate your feedback!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for playing!<br><strong>Adam Nickerson - Adamvision Studios</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/036e7f0d465368e2eae30dd20f6f26f9.poster.avif?t=1745903625\" width=594 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/036e7f0d465368e2eae30dd20f6f26f9.webm?t=1745903625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/036e7f0d465368e2eae30dd20f6f26f9.mp4?t=1745903625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i> </i><br>A throwback to the quarter-munching arcade hits of the '80s, <strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong> is a fast-paced, addictive shoot 'em up with a modern twist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/8c1acbfa8e0b7550c37dbeb9454ce2e0.apng?t=1745903625\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/8c1acbfa8e0b7550c37dbeb9454ce2e0.poster.avif?t=1745903625\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=41 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ship <strong>never stops moving</strong>, turn, boost, and brake to dodge enemies and stay alive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fire automatically</strong> - focus on dodging and collecting power-ups.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gather ammo and power-ups</strong> to unleash devastating attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn coins</strong> to unlock new ships, each with unique speed, fire rate, and shields.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chase high scores</strong> in endless survival mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/43822ef3d3ca31baffe2ef48e0d82bd8.apng?t=1745903625\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/43822ef3d3ca31baffe2ef48e0d82bd8.poster.avif?t=1745903625\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=41 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to Learn, Hard to Master</strong> – Simple controls, deep gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Twin-Stick Needed</strong> – Classic arcade-style movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Massive Power-Ups</strong> – Heat-seekers, lasers, spread shots, bombs, shields, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Ships</strong> – Each with distinct playstyles and advantages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bullet Hell Intensity</strong> – Dodge waves of enemies and projectiles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards & Achievements</strong> – Compete for the top spot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong> – Earn emoticons & profile wallpapers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Cloud Support</strong> – Pick up where you left off.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Languages</strong> – Available in English, Russian, German, Italian, Portuguese, French, Simplified Chinese, and Spanish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Soundtrack by Spiff Tune</strong> – Unique chiptunes for each ship (free DLC).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired by the Best: </strong>Classic hits like <strong>Luftrausers, Asteroids, Space Invaders, Galaxian,</strong> and <strong>Geometry Wars</strong> influence <strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong>’s addictive gameplay and retro charm.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/af15f1c837a8edc3e7adb90689e8980d.apng?t=1745903625\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/af15f1c837a8edc3e7adb90689e8980d.poster.avif?t=1745903625\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=41 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong> is a simple, replayable score-chaser designed for arcade fun. If you find an issue or just want to say hi, reach out via Discord or my website, I appreciate your feedback!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for playing!<br><strong>Adam Nickerson - Adamvision Studios</strong></p>",
